This directory holds certificates shipped with Psi. The files should be in PEM format, and should have the .crt or .pem extension.

Local additions should be made by adding certificates to PSIDATADIR/certs.

Default value of PSIDATADIR:
  Linux, MacOS X and other Unix OS
     ~/.psi/ 
  Mac OS X
     â€¦
  Windows NT, 2000, XP and Server 2003
     %UserProfile%\PsiData\ (usually C:\Documents and Settings\username\PsiData )
  Windows 95, 98 and Me
     %ProgramFiles%\Psi\PsiData\ (usually C:\Program Files\Psi\PsiData )
